00:01:29.510 --> 00:01:31.840
W-What's up with her?! Shouting all of a sudden...

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:34.110
...You've got to be kidding me.

00:01:34.110 --> 00:01:36.960
What is it?

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:41.460
