00:03:11.640 --> 00:03:19.110
Y-Yes. We met for a while at last year's Summer Comiket.

00:03:19.110 --> 00:03:22.410
.....Aah, yes.

00:03:22.410 --> 00:03:24.410
...Phew. Seems like the misunderstanding has been resolved.

