00:03:36.710 --> 00:03:42.340
Hmph, really? How suspicious.

00:03:42.340 --> 00:03:48.190
Kuroneko, what happened? You're much more venomous than usual today.

00:03:48.190 --> 00:03:52.770
...Hmph... I've been telling you from the start.

00:03:52.770 --> 00:04:01.120
Right now I am... the Angel of Vengeance "Yamineko".

